14
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:27,279
<i>[Hi Venus]</i>

15
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:29,840
<i>[Episode 16]</i>

16
00:01:44,199 --> 00:01:47,659
- Yezi, I know now.
- You know what?

17
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:50,419
All the things that Lu Zhaoxi did doesn't show a total disregard for your feelings.

18
00:01:50,419 --> 00:01:52,399
He did those on purpose just to provoke you.

19
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:55,680
- It's like what I wrote in my novel.
- Why did he want to provoke me?

20
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,859
Are you a fool? He likes you.

21
00:01:57,859 --> 00:02:00,020
He wants to know if you like him back.

22
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:02,499
No. He definitely knows you like him.

23
00:02:02,499 --> 00:02:04,139
He just wants you to take the initiative.

24
00:02:04,139 --> 00:02:05,819
That's not possible.

25
00:02:05,819 --> 00:02:08,759
You don't actually think that crappy explanation could fool him.

26
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:11,039
He's a fox.

27
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:15,260
I think you're thinking too much.

28
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:18,240
He even let you buy the dress you liked.

29
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,539
Clearly, the dress was for you to wear.

30
00:02:20,539 --> 00:02:24,438
I'm pretty sure that he lied about getting his ex-girlfriend back.

31
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,638
He's not that childish, is he?

32
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:30,399
Didn't you say that when he isn't working, he's always this childish?

33
00:02:30,399 --> 00:02:34,260
Tomorrow, he'll definitely say that something came up with his ex-girlfriend and he'll let you go over and help.

34
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:37,260
- You can relax.
- Why?

35
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:38,780
I'm not expecting anything.

36
00:02:38,780 --> 00:02:41,959
Oh, please. I know you too well.

37
00:02:44,839 --> 00:02:49,560
If he asks me to go and help, what should I do?

38
00:02:50,839 --> 00:02:52,500
Pretend that you don't know.

39
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:55,360
Put on some airs and play Tai Chi (go to the extreme).

40
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,179
Let's see how he'll act.

